Definition: possession of controlling influence
Example: the deterrent power of nuclear weapons; the power of his love saved her; his powerfulness was concealed by a gentle facade
Synonyms: powerlessness, powerfulness, adj, all, superhuman, powerful, influential, quality, possession, of, controlling, influence, the, deterrent, nuclear, weapons, his, love, saved, her, was, concealed, by, a, gentle, facade
Category: noun.attribute
